{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be futuristic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Legal</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0f1f3f; /* Deep futuristic blue */\n            --secondary-color: #1c335e; /* Slightly lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #e0e0e0; /* Light grey for text */\n            --accent-color: #4da6ff; /* Brighter blue accent */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(77, 166, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(15, 31, 63, 0.8), rgba(28, 51, 94, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/0f1f3f/ffffff?text=Futuristic+Legal') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 31, 63, 0.8), rgba(28, 51, 94, 0.8));\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(77, 166, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(77, 166, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid, .about-content, .contact-info {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .about-text, .contact-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .about-text:hover, .contact-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h3 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            opacity: 0.7;\n        }\n\n        .particles-js {\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero-section p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n            .services-grid, .about-content, .contact-info {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Aura Legal</h1>\n            <p>Illuminating Justice. Innovating Law.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Navigating Tomorrow's Legal Landscape</h2>\n            <p>Cutting-edge legal solutions powered by deep expertise and advanced technology.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Expertise</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-gavel fa-3x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                <p>Strategic legal counsel for businesses of all sizes, from startups to global enterprises.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-robot fa-3x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <h3>Technology & IP</h3>\n                <p>Protecting innovation and navigating the complex legalities of the digital age.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <h3>Compliance</h3>\n                <p>Ensuring adherence to regulations with proactive and robust compliance strategies.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-balance-scale fa-3x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                <p>Assertive representation and strategic dispute resolution for favorable outcomes.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"background-color: var(--secondary-color);\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Aura Legal</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <div class=\"about-text\">\n                    <h3>Pioneering Legal Excellence</h3>\n                    <p>At Aura Legal, we blend a profound understanding of traditional jurisprudence with a forward-thinking approach to technology and innovation. Our team of dedicated legal professionals is committed to providing bespoke solutions that anticipate future challenges and secure your success.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"about-text\">\n                     <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/1c335e/ffffff?text=Our+Team\" alt=\"Our Team\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <div class=\"contact-info\">\n            <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt fa-2x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <p>123 Future Way, Neo City, NC 98765</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-phone fa-2x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <p><a href=\"tel:+15551234567\">(555) 123-4567</a></p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"contact-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-envelope fa-2x\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color);\"></i>\n                <p><a href=\"mailto:info@auralegal.com\">info@auralegal.com</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 Aura Legal. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/particles.js/2.0.0/particles.min.js\"></script>\n    <script>\n        particlesJS(\"particles-js\", {\n            \"particles\": {\n                \"number\": {\n                    \"value\": 80,\n                    \"density\": {\n                        \"enable\": true,\n                        \"value_area\": 800\n                    }\n                },\n                \"color\": {\n                    \"value\": \"#4da6ff\"\n                },\n                \"shape\": {\n                    \"type\": \"circle\",\n                    \"stroke\": {\n                        \"width\": 0,\n                        \"color\": \"#000000\"\n                    },\n                    \"polygon\"